data.description: Welcome to 2322 Shadow Cliff, a remarkable single-story home nestled in the sought-after Oak Hollow Estates. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven boasts not one, but two inviting living areas. The second living space features lofty ceilings and a charming fireplace, ideal for both relaxation and cherished family moments. Delight in the well-appointed eat-in kitchen and a separate dining room for elegant gatherings. The grand Texas-sized master bedroom exudes comfort and luxury. Bedrooms 2 and 3 offer versatile living areas with ample closet space. Revel in the absence of carpet throughout the home. Step outside to a vast backyard adorned with mature trees and a delightful pergola, offering the perfect balance of shade and sunlight. This outdoor oasis sets the stage for entertaining, barbecues, and unwinding after a fulfilling day. The option to include the washer, dryer, and refrigerator adds further convenience to your lifestyle. Benefit from easy access to major highways including 281 and 1604, enhancing your daily commute. Top-tier schools, the YMCA, HEB, a movie theater, an array of restaurants, coffee shops, and shopping destinations are all mere minutes away. Seize the opportunity to experience your dream home - schedule a showing today. Act swiftly, as this gem is poised to be quickly claimed by its fortunate new owner!
